videos.headline: Penn State kicker whiffs on tackle
videos.description: Penn State kicker Joey Julius goes for a big hit on a kickoff, but comes up empty.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State kicker whiffs on tackle) 2016/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: PSU kicker goes after Minnesota LB
videos.description: Penn State kicker Joey Julius and Minnesota LB Jaylen Waters get into a scuffle following a Nittany Lions kickoff.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (PSU kicker goes after Minnesota LB) 2016/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Minnesota LB ejected for leveling PSU kicker
videos.description: After Penn State kicker Joey Julius and Minnesota LB Jaylen Waters got into a scuffle earlier in the game, Waters gets ejected for a hard hit on Julius later in the game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Minnesota LB ejected for leveling PSU kicker) 2016/10/01 ESHEET
